Allows block producers to claim a small reward for evicting a contract. If a block producer fails to do so, a regular users will be allowed to claim the reward. If contract is not evicted as a result of this call, no actions are taken and the sender is not eligible for the reward.destT::AccountIdaux_senderOption<T::AccountId> Instantiates a new contract from the `codehash` generated by `put_code`, optionally transferring some balance.
